
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-xiong-pce-multilayer-lsp-association-02.txt'>
    <title>"PCE Multi-layer LSP Association", Quan Xiong, fangwei hu, Ran Chen</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-xiong-pce-multilayer-lsp-association-02.txt</link>
    <description>The Path Computation Element Communication Protocol (PCEP) provides mechanisms for Path Computation Elements (PCEs) to perform path computations in response to Path Computation Clients (PCCs) requests. [I-D.ietf-pce-association-group] proposed an association mechanism for a set of LSPs.  This document proposes a set of extensions to PCEP to associate a grouping of multi-layer LSPs.  The extensions define a mechanism to create associations between upper-layer LSP and related lower-layer LSPs.</description>
    <dc:date>2018-10-22T07:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
